WEBVTT

00:02.035 --> 00:03.468
<i>Okay, here's the deal.</i>

00:03.737 --> 00:07.138
<i>Your new Council President, Brooke Davis.</i>

00:08.875 --> 00:11.105
I'm totally intimidated by this job.

00:11.277 --> 00:14.644
You're scared of what's in here.
I'm scared of what's out there.

00:14.714 --> 00:17.774
The whole time I was gone
I kept thinking about all this stuff.

00:17.851 --> 00:19.284
Like what kind of stuff?

00:19.352 --> 00:20.683
Mostly being with you.

00:24.457 --> 00:26.982
I love your brother, Dan.
Why won't you leave us alone?

00:27.060 --> 00:29.187
'Cause I didn't pay you
to fall in love with him.

00:29.262 --> 00:32.390
Only you and I know the truth about Jules.
Keith never has to know.

00:32.598 --> 00:35.727
-What do you want from me?
-I'm sure we can work something out.

00:35.802 --> 00:37.064
It's Andy, isn't it?

00:37.137 --> 00:39.469
-What can I do for you?
-Let Lucas go.

00:42.108 --> 00:43.200
Haley?

00:43.476 --> 00:45.808
I'm sorry, Nathan. She's gone.

00:45.879 --> 00:48.814
You realize I wouldn't be
in this situation if it wasn't for you?

00:48.882 --> 00:51.783
If you had stayed at River Court,
I would have never met Haley.

00:51.851 --> 00:54.615
You ruined my life, man.
You better watch your back.

