10:40.673 --> 10:41.731
Which one?

10:41.807 --> 10:46.005
Black bra, black sweater, leather jacket,
Calvins, condoms, underwear optional.

10:46.746 --> 10:49.010
-Have fun.
-Brooke.

10:51.384 --> 10:54.683
You don't think I'm crazy
for wanting to take it slow, do you?

10:55.421 --> 10:57.981
No. I don't think you're crazy.

10:58.758 --> 11:00.282
Now he might.

11:01.427 --> 11:03.657
You'll be fine. You've got good hips.

11:04.463 --> 11:05.930
I'll see you at the party.

11:08.100 --> 11:10.933
Fifty years? Okay.

11:11.237 --> 11:14.104
If you're young and you're watching this...

11:14.173 --> 11:16.471
