11:17.209 --> 11:18.733
Especially if you're a girl.

11:18.911 --> 11:21.277
It's sex, right?

11:22.114 --> 11:25.743
Even 50 years from now,
I'm guessing it's still a really big deal.

11:26.786 --> 11:29.755
It's awkward and threatening.

11:30.589 --> 11:31.681
And thrilling.

11:32.558 --> 11:35.959
But, in a way, it's like sex is the easy part.

11:38.230 --> 11:42.132
Giving your heart to somebody,
that's the scary part.

11:43.202 --> 11:44.260
Trust me.

11:45.271 --> 11:47.637
I understand this mediation is a formality.

11:47.873 --> 11:51.468
But, in my defense, I'm providing a safe
and stable environment for Lucas.

11:52.178 --> 11:53.611
Two-parent. Loving.

11:54.914 --> 11:58.350
That said, I understand sometimes
things aren't always as they appear.

11:59.351 --> 12:01.251
-Your name is Roger?
-Doug.

12:01.787 --> 12:02.776
Doug.

12:04.457 --> 12:07.187
