I've made for my firstborn son.

12:10.730 --> 12:14.063
Yeah, of course, Dan,
but I do have a couple questions.

12:14.767 --> 12:18.100
Can you tell me why you've never paid
any child support to Karen...

12:18.170 --> 12:20.104
