12:25.111 --> 12:27.602
-Financially and otherwise.
-I see.

12:27.680 --> 12:28.738
Ass!

12:29.749 --> 12:32.047
-I'm sorry.
-He's an ass.

12:32.752 --> 12:33.810
Okay.

12:33.886 --> 12:37.549
I didn't take his money,
because to him money is power.

12:37.623 --> 12:40.091
And power is control.
And he would have used it...

12:40.159 --> 12:43.060
