that he always does.

12:43.329 --> 12:46.355
Lucas is my son,
and he has been every day of his life!

12:46.432 --> 12:49.526
And there's not a court
in this country, Dan...

12:49.602 --> 12:52.765
that's going to fall for your ass of a suit...

12:52.838 --> 12:57.298
and your crooked-ass smile
and your assey frat-boy haircut!

13:07.553 --> 13:08.781
Lucas.

13:10.156 --> 13:11.589
Where do you want to live?

13:18.063 --> 13:19.553
