13:19.632 --> 13:22.157
I'm sorry. I lost track of the time.

13:22.401 --> 13:24.835
That's all right.
Me and Jenny have been bonding.

13:29.308 --> 13:30.468
Go to sleep.

13:33.078 --> 13:34.067
How'd it go?

13:36.615 --> 13:37.843
He chose his father.

13:50.362 --> 13:51.590
We're gonna fix this.

13:54.066 --> 13:55.465
I promise you.

13:56.368 --> 13:57.357
Come here.

13:58.871 --> 14:00.270
Promise.

14:03.342 --> 14:04.434
Oh, God.

14:08.447 --> 14:10.039
That's my girl.

14:10.649 --> 14:11.741
