14:12.218 --> 14:14.652
So, I love a party...

14:15.087 --> 14:17.954
but do I know any of these people?

14:18.858 --> 14:20.849
Sure. Look, there's Mouth.

14:25.798 --> 14:27.766
-Hi.
-Hey.

14:29.001 --> 14:31.868
So, everybody looks really drunk.

14:32.137 --> 14:34.867
No, most of them are just stoned.
Come on.

14:37.042 --> 14:38.134
You go.

14:38.978 --> 14:41.173
I'm gonna find a drink.

14:41.814 --> 14:44.009
Okay. In the tub.

14:46.819 --> 14:47.808
