15:23.889 --> 15:25.789
But he called me by my last name.

15:25.858 --> 15:27.689
How great is that?

15:32.932 --> 15:34.524
Nate, thank you for coming.

15:34.900 --> 15:36.765
Whatever. I just ran out of alcohol.

15:41.073 --> 15:43.132
What did you say
in the time capsule, Luke?

15:44.376 --> 15:45.638
Nothing, really.

15:46.478 --> 15:47.945
