16:04.596 --> 16:06.120
Currently, I'm dating...

16:06.932 --> 16:08.297
Brooke Davis.

16:09.268 --> 16:11.862
-What's with you?
-Nothing.

16:13.238 --> 16:15.206
We were just talking
about the time capsule.

16:15.274 --> 16:16.935
About what we said.

16:17.776 --> 16:19.107
Does it really matter?

16:19.345 --> 16:22.212
By the time they open that thing,
we're gonna be old.

16:22.481 --> 16:23.505
Maybe not.

16:23.983 --> 16:26.076
Sometimes they open time capsules early.

16:26.185 --> 16:29.848
When a building moves or there's a fire.
You never know.

16:35.627 --> 16:39.256
Nice wheels outside. A gift from Daddy?

16:44.169 --> 16:45.363
How's Nathan?

16:46.638 --> 16:47.764
Not good.

16:48.841 --> 16:50.274
I know it's none of my business...

16:50.342 --> 16:53.334
but that's your jacket
in Felix's room, right?

16:53.545 --> 16:54.637
Yeah.

16:55.147 --> 16:58.514
