a few minutes ago.

16:59.852 --> 17:00.944
Thanks.

17:02.121 --> 17:03.281
What's going on?

17:03.989 --> 17:05.012
Brother stuff.

17:06.258 --> 17:08.920
Mouth, you're, like, in the A.V. Club
or whatever, right?

17:09.294 --> 17:10.727
Media Club, yeah.

17:13.565 --> 17:17.001
