that I need to erase.

17:17.202 --> 17:18.999
You think you could help me do it?

17:19.471 --> 17:22.531
-Like, tonight?
-You mean break into the school?

17:24.943 --> 17:26.308
Anna, I can't.

17:26.412 --> 17:29.973
Mouth, haven't you ever done something
that you wished you could take back?

17:35.054 --> 17:38.490
Sure. Not too long ago, actually.

17:38.724 --> 17:40.783
What if you had the chance to erase it?

17:44.129 --> 17:45.255
Nathan.

17:46.632 --> 17:47.724
Stop!

17:48.133 --> 17:49.600
Move or I'll run you over.

17:50.402 --> 17:52.029
