18:14.259 --> 18:15.487
I'm not even buzzed.

18:15.561 --> 18:17.290
That's still an open container.

18:17.529 --> 18:18.518
Fine.

18:20.065 --> 18:21.430
What the....

18:36.515 --> 18:39.075
God, I love my life.
Think we can outrun them?

18:39.151 --> 18:41.051
Just pull over. Don't make it worse.

18:41.887 --> 18:43.081
AII right, Luke.

18:43.155 --> 18:47.148
Seeing as how I've already been arrested
once this year, it's been nice knowing you.

19:08.714 --> 19:11.512
Good evening, Officer. Buy us some beer?

19:19.158 --> 19:22.025
Okay, so, I'm a single father...

19:22.094 --> 19:25.530
and, until recently, a high school dropout.

19:25.597 --> 19:29.556
And I'm going on my first date
since my daughter was born.

19:31.236 --> 19:32.635
Am I a great catch, or what?

19:35.974 --> 19:37.202
Are you warm enough?

19:38.477 --> 19:42.345
That's good. Because I had to call in
a few favors to get the breeze just right.

19:42.648 --> 19:43.876
How about the stars?

19:44.049 --> 19:47.382
I told them not to go too heavy,
so it didn't look all movie moment.

19:47.452 --> 19:50.387
More than a million,
less than a billion, that sort of thing.

19:50.656 --> 19:54.183
You wouldn't think just a stroll
down the river would take much planning.

19:54.293 --> 19:57.160
What, are you kidding?
Romantic lighting...

19:57.863 --> 20:01.355
couples scattered about,
music in the distance.

20:01.500 --> 20:04.196
-You're just lucky I'm a cheap date.
-Yeah, I know.

20:06.071 --> 20:08.801
And I am lucky...to be with you tonight.

20:12.945 --> 20:15.778
You know, some guys charge extra
for hand holding.

20:15.981 --> 20:19.075
